Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限的时间里一切都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类孤独的燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界偏离了轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世的火焰包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗  悠二  一点点地把力量集中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:12.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,315}悠二和夏娜和吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀已经能很容易就形成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜   已经到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二点  [零时迷子]啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量能恢复是很好 可这种感觉怎么也...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得适应不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子...有点饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧的重播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧？？是指编造的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要关掉么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理绘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来真疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...为什么那家伙被打了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是因为突然被吻觉得讨厌咯  通常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只因为接吻程度?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程...程度?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...大家看着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕啊...蒂莉艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你们这种行为和夸张的装束才倍受注目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...即将盛开的花朵也需要瞻前仰后么 须德奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身份不过是受我的[摇篮花园]庇护之身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望你用这自以为是的态度对我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂.喂...蒂莉艾尔...我可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...哥哥....但是 请再稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么[自在式]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥在找的东西似乎快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易发现的东西 却被某些人带着逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂不是前功尽弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防他们逃掉而把他们关在我们的[摇篮]里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了   哥哥  除那个以外请享用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...你知道[八音盒]吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[八音盒]？是指音乐盒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...通常是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过[八音盒]的叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是更贴近它的发音方式更高雅么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是为了和这个[自在法]一起制造围墙的[宝器]吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着十分不错的音色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还搞什么躲避球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨真大啊...但是能中止真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样再继续下去的话可就糟了   一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头？？那是谁啊？？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重伤啊...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于平井...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有...只是经常和你一起来校...那个...什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好象有点什么事...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...没什么没什么...什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只是接吻也无所谓...果然还是不能就轻易就原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...我了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是原谅了的话...之后就会没完没了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢...我觉得吻很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？？你说得是那个意思啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...说得也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻？？昨天悠二也是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学到的东西应该是没错的...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么...在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在查什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 不是什么了不起的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚也说了嘛...和平井只是关系好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有恋爱关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐...我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...吵得我头疼欲裂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊。。受伤的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只是被球打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启作  荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌倦酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么问这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似简单实际上是很难的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你说查过了的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然在图书馆看书查过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是和以前知道的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道怎么应对也见过 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是？？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现我所知道的和大家所想的意义好象完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想千草阿姨可能知道那个意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过小说或是文学作品了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那些加入了个人的主观的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对恰当的分析和理论的思索无用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔斯托尔曾经说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯托尔是在远方的你的父亲代理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有卓越的见解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...但是呢...夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢...夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下...光是凭那些理论是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料上面所记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是严正的事实和理论 除此之外没有别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是夏娜想到的东西却是那以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是种含糊的没有绝对答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心和感情的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心和感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的彼此身体的抚摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是亲密的感情的表示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...接吻也是这些动作中的一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握手啊...拥抱啊  大家都这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...虽然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...如果是和阿拉斯托尔先生这么做是没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...但是能和小悠这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新好好想想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会觉得不好意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那种事的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且虽说是吻...吻脸和吻嘴意义相当不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和悠二嘴对嘴...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样太讨厌了...我可不想被那样...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吻可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是即使是阿拉斯托尔也不能做的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜...我是这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴对嘴的接吻是类似于誓言的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓言？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 用自己的一切起誓都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交付自己的一切都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就这样结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了[零时迷子]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量一到零点的时候就会恢复到原来是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...是不是也可以理解成我不会变老?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己去验证啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也许会花很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想是不是可以和夏娜一直在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托你们一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草阿姨...我借下电话用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用吧...但是...夏娜...该去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  嗯 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草阿姨...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我的？？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初闻贵声...夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名叫阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...阿拉斯托尔先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井紫一直承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是坂井悠二的母亲千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此 多谢您长时间的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  特地打电话来是有什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井紫的事我一直都有看着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...你不妨叫那孩子叫夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也习惯那样叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀...是阿拉斯托尔认同的昵称啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...嗯 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我要说的事是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是昨天的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下...小悠 夏娜 快去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是要否定夫人您的恋爱观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但希望您以后不要说像昨天那样的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦...是我强行问出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜连那种话都向您说了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明您很得她的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一直疼爱着她把她抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个十分纯洁的好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此想请您以后慎重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昨天那样想诱使她和坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生不慎的接触的言论请不要再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白您的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人您真明事理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样您能体谅我的忧虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...为了夏娜可以再和您谈一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 正如您所说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个自尊心强力量很强的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是另一方面 我觉得也有幼小脆弱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有对人的心情和人心十分不适和无防备的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的悠二第一次因为年轻势头而想要强迫她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁的那孩子能做多少抵抗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我感到了那样的危险...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还太早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再让她过些年...让她体验各种各样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地教导她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题不会配合我们的情况出现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得把应该教的东西教授于她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在太早的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是为了夏娜自身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且女孩子也比外表要早熟得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能收回我提出的欠考虑的请求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了冒失的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜的话 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地教那孩子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该能按自己的做法找到正确的答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有那种信赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近了 近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 好象在找什么一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真不愧是索拉托的[欲望的嗅觉]啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种让人不爽的感觉...一定是弗来姆黑兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在哪里 在哪里 弗来姆黑兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快点弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经快被感觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 那也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道遇到弗来姆黑兹也只是时间早晚的问题而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把陷阱再挖深一点  我要做到万无一失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先去打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找出来是很容易的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚刚阿拉斯托尔在电话中说昨天的事什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不和你 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话...这个是为了坂井做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我？？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一直只是吃饭团...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃哪个呢 真犹豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 买得还相当多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂止是相当多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才刚开始买
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这关键的时候又出现了不速之客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐？？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啦...美丽的杀掠者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这软弱无能的色情男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀...你的熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...介绍给你吧 蒂莉艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗来姆黑兹中也是首屈一指的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[悼词咏唱者]玛乔丽.铎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那就是 [蹂躏的爪牙]的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些人没有我想要的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 简单地就发现了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和猎物不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然哥哥这么说了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙不是徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么放走好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是放他们走的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我让她放他们走的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 白痴玛鲁科
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来和妈妈说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你该在意的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来   多用点心在锻炼上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要给妈妈丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...
